{
  "_doc": "Curated competitor logo overrides. Use this for teams whose Liquipedia auto-resolution returns the wrong logo, no logo, or where you want to set a specific brand_color the resolver can't infer. For *exhaustive* coverage of every team in the DB, use `pnpm --filter @oddzilla/db db:resolve-logos` instead — it queries Liquipedia's MediaWiki API for each active competitor across the 15 supported esports. Entries here are matched against `competitors` by (sport_slug, competitor_slug); slugs follow feed-ingester's slugify rule (lowercase, non-alnum runs collapsed to '-'). Logo URLs verified by fetching live Liquipedia listings on 2026-05-05. Apply via `pnpm --filter @oddzilla/db db:seed-logos`.",
